---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const LAUNCH_DATE = '2026-05-27';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Shipping | OddlyWiredCo"
  description="OddlyWiredCo shipping information: production time, UK and international delivery estimates, tracking, customs and lost-parcel policy."
>
  <section class="fold light">
    <div class="container legal">
      <p class="meta">Legal · Shipping</p>
      <h1 class="h-mono lg">Shipping</h1>
      <p class="effective">Effective {LAUNCH_DATE}. Last updated {LAUNCH_DATE}.</p>

      <h2>Production time</h2>
      <p>
        Every item is made to order. Our print partner (Printify) typically produces journals,
        mugs and stickers in <strong>2–5 working days</strong> from order confirmation. Production
        time is separate from shipping time.
      </p>

      <h2>Delivery estimates</h2>
      <p>Total time from order confirmation to delivery, including production:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>United Kingdom</strong> — 5–10 working days</li>
        <li><strong>European Union</strong> — 10–15 working days</li>
        <li><strong>United States &amp; Canada</strong> — 10–18 working days</li>
        <li><strong>Rest of world</strong> — 15–25 working days</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These are estimates, not guarantees. Carriers occasionally have delays we cannot control,
        especially around UK and US public holidays.
      </p>

      <h2>Shipping cost</h2>
      <p>
        Shipping is calculated at checkout based on your delivery address. The exact cost is shown
        before you confirm payment.
      </p>

      <h2>Where we ship from</h2>
      <p>
        Orders are dispatched from our print partner's UK facility (Prodigi) for UK and most EU
        addresses, and from their US facility for North American and rest-of-world addresses,
        whichever route is cheaper and faster for the destination.
      </p>

      <h2>Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        You receive a dispatch email with a tracking link once your order leaves the print facility.
        Tracking detail varies by carrier — for international shipments tracking sometimes pauses
        between systems, this is normal.
      </p>

      <h2>Customs and import duty</h2>
      <p>
        For deliveries outside the UK and EU you may be charged import duty, taxes or handling fees
        by your country's customs service. These are payable by you and are not included in the
        price you pay us. We declare the actual value of the goods on the customs label.
      </p>

      <h2>Lost or missing parcels</h2>
      <p>
        If your parcel has not arrived within the upper end of the delivery estimate (10 working
        days UK, 25 working days international), email
        <a href="mailto:hello@oddlywiredco.com">hello@oddlywiredco.com</a> with your order number.
        We will investigate with the carrier and replace or refund per our
        <a href="/legal/returns">returns policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Incorrect address</h2>
      <p>
        Please check your delivery address carefully at checkout. Items returned to sender because
        of an incorrect or incomplete address can be reshipped at your cost; if you do not respond
        to our reshipment email within 14 days we cannot refund the order.
      </p>

      <p class="back"><a href="/">← Back to OddlyWiredCo</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal { max-width: 720px; }
  .legal .meta { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .legal h1 { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .legal .effective {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--owc-ink);
  }
  .legal p, .legal li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .legal ul { margin: 4px 0 12px 24px; }
  .legal a {
    color: var(--owc-ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--owc-pulse);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .legal a:hover { background: var(--owc-pulse); }
  .legal .back {
    margin-top: 48px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  }
  .legal .back a { border-bottom: none; }
</style>
